OL,3,CLabour appears to haemorrhage seats as
OL,4,Cfirst local election results roll in
OL,6,FLabour appeared to be haemorrhaging
OL,7,Fcouncil seats in local elections
OL,8,Facross England as initial results
OL,9,Fpointed towards Reform UK gains.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer's party went into
OL,12,FThursday's local elections expected to
OL,13,Flose up to 1,850 councillors, with
OL,14,Fsenior figures describing the contest
OL,15,Fas "tough".
OL,17,FInitial results painted a bleak
OL,18,Fpicture for the Prime Minister, with
OL,19,FLabour losing councillors in its
OL,20,Ftraditional northern heartlands.
OL,26,@wD@DOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
