OL,3,CLabour appears to haemorrhage seats as
OL,4,Cfirst local election results roll in
OL,6,FIn Halton, in Cheshire, Labour held
OL,7,Ftwo of the 17 seats it was defending
OL,8,Fas Reform UK gained 15 councillors in
OL,9,Fthe first council to complete its
OL,10,Fcount on Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn some wards, Reform won with more
OL,13,Fthan 50% of the vote in an area where
OL,14,Flast year Nigel Farage's party won the
OL,15,FRuncorn and Helsby by-election by just
OL,16,Fsix votes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
