OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778213055
OL,3,CLabour appears to haemorrhage seats as
OL,4,Cfirst local election results roll in
OL,6,FHe said: "We are used to, in our
OL,7,Flifetimes, Labour or the Conservative
OL,8,FParty winning majorities in general
OL,9,Felections with north of 40% of the
OL,10,Fvote.
OL,12,F"And I think now, they are going to
OL,13,Fstruggle to get 40% between them, and
OL,14,FI don't think they're coming back."
OL,16,FEarly results also showed Reform
OL,17,Fsuccess further south, with the party
OL,18,Fpicking up seats in Brentwood, in
OL,19,FEssex.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
