OL,3,CLabour appears to haemorrhage seats as
OL,4,Cfirst local election results roll in
OL,6,FThe Greens are also expected to do
OL,7,Fwell, with new leader Zack Polanski
OL,8,Fpredicting "record-breaking local
OL,9,Felections" for the party, while Sir Ed
OL,10,FDavey's Liberal Democrats are eyeing
OL,11,Fan eighth successive year of local
OL,12,Fgains.
OL,14,FBut it could be another bad night for
OL,15,Fthe Conservatives despite an
OL,16,Fimprovement in party leader Kemi
OL,17,FBadenoch's approval rating, with the
OL,18,Fparty expected to lose further ground
OL,19,Fto Reform.
OL,26,@pD@LOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
