OL,3,CLabour appears to haemorrhage seats as
OL,4,Cfirst local election results roll in
OL,6,FLabour faces losing the national vote
OL,7,Fin Wales for the first time in more
OL,8,Fthan a century, while in Scotland the
OL,9,FSNP appears likely to remain the
OL,10,Flargest party after 19 years in power.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
